reviews.review_text: This is the store located on 531 North Road Coquitlam. I was very hungry, I did my order over the self orders. , the panel of orders was almost full, suddenly the store got crowded, but the head of Staff I believe her name was something like Herman, she looked at the orders and collected all the staff talked with them gave them instructions and boon within few minutes starting calling the numbers, not to mention before that she was dealing with some cleanups customers with small kids. Overall she well deserves the title of the manager even more. Not to mention at all times she was talking to customers or answering questions,her beautiful smile captured you. Thank you for your heard works. Most appreciated.

It was a few days ago that I witnessed this employee take my order, she was the most sweetness girl ever, had a big smile on her face, also made sure that read me back my order, to make sure it was correct. But she was the only one that I really saw her busting her butt. The employee name was lena. She is such a sweetheart   I cant wait to come back.
Best McDonalds Ive eaten at in a while. The employees actually care about their customers and the quality of food theyre serving.
food was very okay, but the CUSTOMER SERVICE i got from this one employee named ABID was top notch! treated me like a princess from start to finish.

Usually you know what youre getting when you hit a McDonalds, but we had a really good experience at this location. The staff were super friendly, waaay more then I expected from minimum wage employees, and our food was just about perfect, it wasnt smashed together and thrown in the bag like normal which was an awesome surprise.
i was in the drive thru the other day. the guy who took my order was so cool good vibes, his name was abiid i think not sure but 10/10 service. Food
Its a McDonalds. Not as busy as some other ones. Live that thye have pineapple chunks in the Happy Meals now.
10/10. the food was phenominal. view is amazing. free wifi. slayed.
I ordered the Among Us Happy Meal with extra Sussy Sauce and they delivered it nice and hot in a timely manner. My child is extremely happy with his Sussy Meal, and so am I. Thank you McDonalds.
Good atmosphere for gathering. Staff too busy and very unorganized.
Fast service and friendly staff and location easy to get in and out.
Tried bts meal  fast service and quality consistent. Mc nugget is not so good  well I just order to try the bts sauce this time. I prefer Cajun sauce! Sausage Mc muffin is always good though.
Honestly the best place I ve ever been. Should have a higher review. Great view of Burquitlam skytrain

Great ambience with multiple options available for Non-Veg and Unlike other stores they also have Veg burgers to try. Vegetarian options: They have new Vieggie Burger available Veg Crispy. Its delicious Parking: Ample number of stops Kid-friendliness: Various drinks and dessert options to choose for kids Wheelchair accessibility: Easily accessible

I came here on monday and i loved the food. Food was hot. Very friendly service here . I want to mention a name of one of the manager working at that time, her name was Navpreet. She was so nice to me. Also offered my food to the table.      Such a nice person    i love u girl    U are the best highly recommended place
They serve the best iced coffee ever!!! It s my favorite branch to get it every day, they just never disappoint! Also their Wi-Fi is really good. Best McDonalds ever!!

Made an order from the app before heading over. When I arrived, the app was having trouble taking the payment. I asked if I could pay there, and without missing a beat the staff were able to take debit at the till. I went over to get my drink, and heard my food being called already. Since I was still pouring, the staff brought it over to me. I was out the door with my food much faster than I expected. I hadnt had McDonalds in a while and the food was just as expected. Better than any fast food experience needed to be.

An employee messed up my order, I complained to the management, and Ronald McDonald himself came over, took the employee to the back of the restaurant, then shot them in the back of the head. Three times. Rest of the the workers seemed very motivated to make my order correct. Thank you Ronald for doing a good job with my food :D

I come through this drive thru every week day morning to get my regular special breakfast. Every other McDonald s cannot seem to get it right but 9/10 Rachel serves me and she s such a delight. Such a sweet woman! Very humble and soft spoken. Not rude at all. Always makes sure that everything was entered right. Someone I would be friends with and I cannot say that about any other fast food service worker. Thanks Rachel for making the mornings a enjoyable breeze

There was a problem in refunding the order, and one of the employees (Narveep K.) She was curtious, handled the situation very well and fixed things rather quickly So I wanted to mention her name Very good customer support
A well run Mcdonalds never disappoints

Service is fast as usual.  Staff always friendly and polite, coffee is always good for a $1, restaurant is clean. Please, please move the sign(s) that restrict vision for drivers pulling out to Clarke Rd.

This is the most consistent Mc Donald s in B.C.  99% of the time the fries have just the right crunch. The others in the area have a 50/50 chance of getting soggy fries. Who ever manages this location you get a big thumbs up

The manager here was a sweet asian-canadian lady who kindly offered a couple burger patties for my dog.   Service was fast and great, and with her in charge with her great customer service and smile, this location should do well.
The speed was great! I ordered Soft serve for some weird reason but, it only took them a few mins to get it done .
This is the best McDonalds around and it aint even close, seriously Id go here everyday if I lived by it and Im not a fat dude
